* nunit-gtk
------------

nunit-gtk is a frontend for running NUnit 2 test suites.

* Directory layout
-------------------

	AUTHORS
	NEWS
	README
	ChangeLog
	makefile.gnu

	src/
		Source files for nunit-gtk.
	art/
		Actually this directory should be called pseudo-random-art.
		It contains a few PNG images used in nunit-gtk.


Installing nunit-gtk
----------------------

Just run:

	make -f makefile.gnu install prefix=YOURPREFIX

You need Gtk# and NUnit2.

* Running nunit-gtk
---------------------

	mono nunit-gtk.exe [assembly name or filename]


-Gonzalo

